                  <summary>Pentateuch, (Genesis through Deuteronomy), አምስቱ፡ ብሔረ፡ ኦሪት፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="149r" facs="002">Fols 1r–149r</locus><title>Orit</title>
